org.jikesrvm.compilers.opt.ir.ia32

Class PhysicalRegisterSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jikesrvm.compilers.opt.ir.GenericPhysicalRegisterSet
      • org.jikesrvm.compilers.opt.ir.ia32.PhysicalRegisterSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BitSetMapping

    public final class PhysicalRegisterSet
extends GenericPhysicalRegisterSet
    This class represents a set of Registers corresponding to the IA32 register set.
